                        <condition>
                           <list>
                              <item>
                                 <p>Vellum, about 8 1/8 in. by 5 3/4, consisting of 66 leaves, some
                                    of which are much stained and others slightly torn, especially
                                    foll. 1— 7, 18, 19, 52, 57, 59, and 60. The quires, signed with
                                    letters, are now only 7 in number. Leaves are wanting at the
                                    beginning and end, and also after fol. 63. There are from 21 to
                                    27 lines in each page. </p>
                              </item>
                           </list>
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
